    "Three responses had significant disagreement (defined as ≥ 2 on the Likert scale) between the two raters which required the involvement of a third rater.",
    "There were 9 FAQs relating to general and procedurerelated queries for TKR (Table 2).",
    "Of the responses, 7/9 (77.8%) were classified as accurate (mean grade 4.5), and 9/9 (100%) were classified as relevant (mean grade 4.9).",
    "Responses to two procedure-related questions: \"Do I need to fast before a total knee replacement?\"",
    "and \"Will I be awake during a total knee replacement?\""
